Usage: write_tcf [-help] [<file>] [-block <string>]
                 [-exclude_hier_insts <string>] [-macro_output] [-pin]
                 [-primary_input] [-seq_output]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
<file>                           # file name (string, optional)
-block <string>                  # dump block level duty and activity
                                 # (string, optional)
-exclude_hier_insts <string>     # -excludeHierInsts <hier-inst-list>
                                 # (string, optional)
-macro_output                    # macro output only (bool, optional)
-pin                             # pin format (bool, optional)
-primary_input                   # primary input only (bool, optional)
-seq_output                      # sequential output only (bool, optional)